---
title: Tex-Mex Chicken Enchilada Bowls with Chicken Thighs, Zesty Rice, Pico de Gallo & Spiced Crema
description: Rice bowls are one of our go-to dinnertime staples. And why not? They’re hearty, flavorful, and so versatile. This version’s got bold ’n’ saucy chicken thighs served over a bed of fluffy lime rice, topped with fresh salsa, Monterey Jack cheese, and Southwest crema. Yep, this blissful bowl is sure to satisfy.
